\nParameters:\n\n- max_linelen\n  : Has the same meaning as for \"compress()\" function.\n- max_rules_per_file\n  : Internet Explorers \\<= 9 have an artificial max number of rules per CSS\n    file (4096; <http://blogs.msdn.com/b/ieinternals/archive/2011/05/14/10164546.aspx>)\n    When `max_rules_per_file` is a positive number, the function *always* returns\n    a list of `str` objects, each limited to contain less than the passed number\n    of rules.\n\n    - preserve_exclamation_comments\n      : Has the same meaning as for \"compress()\" function.\n\nAlways returns a `list` of `str` objects with compressed CSS.\n"]}], "variables": [{"name": "csscompressor.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "csscompressor._url_re", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "csscompressor._calc_re", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "csscompressor._hsl_re", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "csscompressor._ws_re", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "csscompressor._str_re", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "csscompressor._yui_comment_re", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "csscompressor._ms_filter_re", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "csscompressor._spaces1_re", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "csscompressor._spaces2_re", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "csscompressor._ie6special_re", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "csscompressor._charset1_re", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "csscompressor._charset2_re", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "csscompressor._dirs_re", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "csscompressor._pseudo_re", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "csscompressor._common_funcs_re", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "csscompressor._common_val_funcs_re", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "csscompressor._space_and_re", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "csscompres